### Latest projects

1. [KMB ETA (Estimated Time Arrival) Java API](https://github.com/mob41/KmbETA-API)  [Latest Release](https://github.com/mob41/KmbETA-API/releases)

3. HomeAutoSys (Home Automation System)
  - Awaiting DNA-Kit for SDK
4. HomeDashboard (HomeAutoSys's Mobile UI)

### Future Projects
-  (Future) HomeAdminboard (HomeAutoSys's Admin UI)
-  (Future) KmbETA Android App
-  (Future) KmbETA iOS App

### About Me
I am just new in Java but also good at Java. I started programming since I was 8. I am teen now. I am working on the project for my house's Home Automation System. I am currently awaiting for DNA-Kit from Broadlink, for API embedding on the HomeAutoSys.
